signInUrl.description:
Full URL or path to navigate on "Add another account" action.
Multi-session mode only.
signInUrl.name: signInUrl

showName.description: Controls if the user name is displayed next to the trigger button
showName.name: showName

afterSignOutUrl.description: Full URL or path to navigate after sign out is complete
afterSignOutUrl.name: afterSignOutUrl

afterMultiSessionSingleSignOutUrl.description:
Full URL or path to navigate after signing out the current user is complete.

afterMultiSessionSingleSignOutUrl.name: afterMultiSessionSingleSignOutUrl

afterSwitchSessionUrl.description:
Full URL or path to navigate after successful account change.
Multi-session mode only.
afterSwitchSessionUrl.name: afterSwitchSessionUrl
